msgid ""
"The :kl-ref:`SceneWrapper` interface is the main interface for "
"abstracting a source scene (such as the "
":ref:`SceneGraph<scenegraph_overview>`). It allows to create generic "
"evaluation contexts (:kl-ref:`SWContext`), queries and reference arrays."
