" types, such as :kl-ref:`SGDirectionalLight` and :kl-ref:`SGInstance`, to"
" corresponding RTR objects, such as :kl-ref:`RTRDirectionalLight` and "
":kl-ref:`RTRSWInstance`. See :ref:`scenehub_adaptors` for more details "
